## ðŸ’¡ Project Overview

**"Can't we solve complex transfer procedures with a single line of chat?"**

Existing mobile banking apps require users to go through numerous steps and input processes to send money. OnelineBank is a fintech solution that introduces a **Conversational UI** to solve this inconvenience.

When a user expresses their intention to send money in everyday language, the app analyzes it and automatically executes the transfer process. We maximized usability by **incorporating the familiar experience of 'chatting' into financial services.**

